Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:09.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ブロック発動だ\N人の目もクソもない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Activate it! Activate the block!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:11.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't care who's watching! Bury him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:11.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,潰すんだ 奴を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:13.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ブロック発動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:16.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The block is activated! Does Kaiji have any chance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:15.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なりふり構わぬ手段を\N取ってきた一条に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:18.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打つ手はあるのか カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:18.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,now that Ichijou casts off the illusion of a fair game!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:20.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:21.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:25.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　絶体絶命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:25.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji is cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:45.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１玉たりとも通さぬ非情な門番
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:45.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The stern guards turn away every ball he shoots!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右打ちも不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:47.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Bouncing off the right is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:51.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クルーンへの道は\Nすべて閉ざされた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:51.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All of the paths to the trays have been closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:51.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)\pos(640,505)}Fruitless Achievement
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.49,0:00:53.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're completely sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完全封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:03.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　最初の1000万を\N打ち尽くす　溶かす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:03.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's first ten million has been blown! It's melted away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:13.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ\Nどうも流れが悪いようですね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:13.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems like you're not doing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:16.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく意気込んで\N来店してくださったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.79,0:01:16.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Such a pity, you seemed so excited when you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがに手じまいですかね\N残念です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:20.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I suppose this is goodbye, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:23.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 言ってる\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:22.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:28.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続行だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:26.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:30.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Gimme another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:30.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,追加 もう１枚\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:38.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Another card. Hurry it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.43,0:01:38.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１枚だ　早くしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:41.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長\Nん…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:43.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,換えてやれ\Nあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:42.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.44,0:01:46.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:44.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:48.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's his plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:49.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.95,0:01:51.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ いくぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:51.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:55.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右打ちなんてしねえ\Nあくまで中央
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:57.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not even gonna shooting to the right. I'm going straight down the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:59.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中央から強行突破だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:58.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna break though by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:13.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで無駄なことするんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why is he wasting his balls like this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:16.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのパクパクがインチキで\Nはじくって分かってるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:16.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He should know those flippers are rigged!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:18.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おかしくなったんじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:18.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Something's not right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:21.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:20.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どう考えたっておかしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:23.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,客たちの言うとおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The customers are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:26.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ こんな不毛なことを続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why is he wasting his money with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:28.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What is he planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:29.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を企んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:31.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is just cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:31.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひでえな しかし\Nう…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:34.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I know it's supposed to be rigged, but this is pushing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:34.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,締めるっていっても限度があるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:37.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't just block it off completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:38.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただの１発も通さねえなんて\N許されるのか こんなインチキ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:39.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is really taking it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:42.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひでえ　めちゃくちゃだ\N店長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:41.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:42.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:49.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it. He thinks I'll have to remove the block due to the audience reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:46.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これか\Nこの見物人の空気に負けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:49.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がブロックを\N解除せざるを得なくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:52.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He thinks I'll fall for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:52.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう踏んでいるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:59.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He thinks I'll change it back to the normal 1/3 odds?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:56.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このまま続けていれば\Nいつか戻すだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:03:00.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常の３分の１の確率に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that a guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:05.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう読み 計算か
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Or a calculation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:08.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン　バカが　緩めるものか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:08.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Whatever! I'm not going to waver!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:13.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前はこのまま死ぬ 不毛に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:12.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're going to die a pointless death!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:18.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pointless! Pointless! Pointless! Pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:19.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不毛に　不毛に　不毛に　不毛に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不毛に死ね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:21.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Die for no reason at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:24.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:28.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm lucky he's doing this in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:28.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助かったぜ 今が昼のさなかで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:32.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There are three times as many people here at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜に比べてギャラリーも\N３分の１程度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これなら問題はない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:36.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These few shouldn't cause any problems, no matter how ruthless we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:36.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらがむごく勝っても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:41.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長 あちらの方々がお話があると\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:37.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:41.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You have a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:47.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジを確保するために\N本部から派遣された方々とか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:45.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the group sent from HQ to retrieve Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:53.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　奴のタイムリミットは\N４時だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:48.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His time's up at 4, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:56.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご苦労さまです\Nいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:54.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:55.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:04:00.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry. As soon as we barricade the doors, he has no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:04:00.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題ありませんよ\Nドアさえ固めれば奴は袋のネズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:04.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし暴れるようでしたら\N私どもも手伝います
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:04.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he causes any trouble, I'd be glad to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:06.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その点はご心配なく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:09.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That won't be necessary. But we do have an order from HQ for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それよりも本部から\N要請がありまして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,From HQ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本部から？\Nはい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:15.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このフロアに仕掛けられた\N複数のカメラ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:17.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They want to use footage from the security cameras
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:17.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それらで撮影している映像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:21.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,to broadcast Kaiji's last game live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:21.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの勝負をライブ中継として\N送信しろとのことです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:24.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライブで？一体どこへです？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Live? Broadcast where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地下\N地下？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:26.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:35.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The audience will be Teiai's underground forced labor camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:35.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,送信先は\N帝愛熔工 地下強制労働施設
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take a short break!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:48.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一時 休憩とする\N休憩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A break?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:51.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昼休みには まだ早いぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's too early for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:06.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと５時間だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Five hours left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:11.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In five hours, just five hours, we find out whether Kaiji pulled it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:11.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと５時間で… あと５時間で\Nカイジさんの成否が決まる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:13.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うなって\Nだってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:12.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't even say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:17.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if he didn't, we're all—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:16.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それはつまり その… 俺たちの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:20.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってんだよ そんなことは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:19.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You think I don't know that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:23.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも言ったって\Nどうなるもんでもないし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:23.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But talking about it isn't going to help anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:30.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第一 考え出したら\N苦しくなるだろ 息が
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:28.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just mentioning it makes it hurt to even breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:35.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たださえ息が上がってるのに\Nますます…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:34.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,My chest just keeps getting tighter and tighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:37.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,三好　大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:37.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you okay!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,—What's wrong!? Are you okay!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,—Miyoshi! Miyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:41.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,三好 三好 しっかりしろ　おい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:40.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:44.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,苦しい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不安で押し潰されそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The anxiety is killing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:50.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪かった　俺が悪かった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:49.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! It's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:52.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji... Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:53.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:55.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:01.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here we go. {We get signal. Main screen turn on.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:06.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入りました\NＡＢＣ　３カメラ正常です
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:05.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Cameras A, B, and C are working fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:09.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＤＥＦ　すべて切り替わりました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can switch through D, E, and F fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:33.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ？おお 懐かしい懐かしい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:35.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:35.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしもやったぞ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:39.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the one I hit the 3-billion jackpot on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:39.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何せ30億という\N大当たりだったからのう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:45.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆 驚愕放心　びっくりしてのう\Nエヘヘヘ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:44.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone was so shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:50.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ みんなも飲んで飲んで\N遠慮せず
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:50.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Drink up, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:54.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're comrades! Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:55.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我らは同じ同胞　兄弟だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:07:00.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,制裁\Nあっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:06:59.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Punish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:03.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やる気なく｢はあ｣と言った貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:05.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Punish him for that listless "yes, sir!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:06.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,制裁\Nあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:08.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sir, I didn't mean to—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:08.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや あの 私は別に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:13.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兄弟とはいえ序列はあるのだ\N圧倒的に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:13.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There is an order among brothers! An inviolable order!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:16.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… いや その\N会長　すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:18.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sir! I really didn't mean to offend you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私はそんなつもりでは\N会長　会長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:23.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アハハ　さあ 飲んで飲んで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now drink! Drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい！いただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:26.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:33.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アハハ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:43.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええな ええな アハハ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:41.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:49.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! This is Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:49.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君　カイジ君じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:53.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He still hasn't learned his lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:53.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっとるのう\N相変わらずバカなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:56.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆の衆　よく見ておけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:56.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take a close look, gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:08:01.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's got more guts than it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:08:01.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男 こう見えて\Nなかなかの つわものでのう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:08.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And here he is risking his life on the outside in his last gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:05.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このつわものがシャバでの存命\N己の人生を懸けて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:08.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の大勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:12.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この土壇場 どうジタバタするのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's his final moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:15.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Watch how he struggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:15.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それをよく見ておくのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:18.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後学のために　な？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:18.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You may need the example someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:21.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… はい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:25.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ　壊れてる壊れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:25.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's crumbling, he's crumbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:28.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ するのかのう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why does he do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:35.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This ruinous, murderous, self-destructive gambling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:32.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破滅 死滅 自滅覚悟の愚行を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:37.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウヒヒ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:43.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:51.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ どうして\N無駄なことを続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why does he continue his fruitless battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:54.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見物人たちの あきれにも似た感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:54.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The audience seem to have given up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:05.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここが正念場だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:04.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's do or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待つしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:10.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All we can do is wait and endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:11.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は ただ耐え\Nノックし続けるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:12.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All we can do is keep knocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:19.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Keep knocking on the door of high-stakes gambling, hoping Lady Luck will open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:20.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この一か八かの博打を\N勝利へと導く運命のドア
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:24.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can't open the door. All we can do is wait for it to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらからは開けない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:27.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのドアが開くまで ただ待つ\Nノックの手を休めず
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:30.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can't stop until we're physically incapable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:30.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしノックが実らず\Nドアが開かなければ それまで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:35.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが俺と奴の天運 宿運
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:34.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is our fate, our destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:42.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,賭けは散り 沈む
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:42.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We lose, and fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:48.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沈まざるを得ない\N王国という あの地獄へ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can do nothing but fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:47.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fall down into that abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:52.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's do or die, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:52.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここが正念場だ カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:04.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん\N今頃どうしてるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:03.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Kaiji's doing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:09.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He probably just took the money and decided to go out with a bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:06.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とっくに金はスッちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:10.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ漫然と残り時間を\N過ごしているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:14.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We haven't heard from him in so long. That's probably what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:15.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと音沙汰なしなんだから\Nその可能性が一番高いけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハア
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:26.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でもカイジさんなら\Nもしかして… もしかして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:26.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But what if? What if Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:35.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Early lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:35.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少し早いが昼飯を配っておく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:42.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？\N何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:42.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:46.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本来 休憩時間中に\Nテレビを鑑賞するなど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:48.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Usually, watching television on break is forbidden underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:50.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この地下では許されない\Nあり得ないシャバっ気
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:53.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An impossible luxury for the denizens of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:55.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわつく地獄の住人たち
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:11:00.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Today, President Hyodo will visit this facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:11:00.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日はたまたま この施設に\N兵藤会長がお見えになっている
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:05.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The President is giving you this special opportunity to watch TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:05.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その会長のご厚意で特別に\Nテレビ中継を見ることが許された
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:10.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll be showing a live broadcast that's very important to a few of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:10.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この中の何人かにとっては\N非常に興味深い中継となるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Live?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中継？\Nサッカーか野球か
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Soccer? Baseball, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:17.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフ　覚えている者も多いはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:21.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Most of you should remember the man who left on furlough three weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:21.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３週間ほど前 この施設から\N一時外出した男のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:24.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\Nカイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:24.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お…\Nおい あいつか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:29.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの大槻を倒したとかっていう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The man who took down Ohtsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:31.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:31.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつがどうかしたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:36.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right now, he's gambling in a Teiai casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:36.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その男が今 我が帝愛グループの\N経営するカジノで勝負をしている
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:39.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんが？\N勝負を？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:39.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,—Gambling!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:44.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むろん 彼自身と ここにいる\N何人かの解放をかけてだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:44.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's betting his own release, and some of yours as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:48.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えー\Nマジですか それ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:52.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の目で確かめてみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:50.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,See for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:55.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,映ります
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:59.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あ… マジかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:59.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is this really happening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:07.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:05.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん\Nカイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:07.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:10.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:14.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's risking it all for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:14.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんが\N俺たちのために勝負を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:23.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, he's playing pachinko!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:23.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待て　カイジさんが\Nやってるこれって… パチンコ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:28.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:36.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell!? We put up more than 60 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:36.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちの借金は全部で\N6000万を超えるんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:39.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今更 パチンコなんかして\Nどうするんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:39.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he playing Pachinko for!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことなんだ カイジさん\N前田さん　落ち着けって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:41.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,—What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:41.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,—Calm down, Maeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's right, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:44.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも前田さんの言うとおりだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:48.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パチンコなんかで\N俺たちの借金分を稼ぐなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:48.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pachinko will never pay out enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと無理な話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He may as well not bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:53.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでもない\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:52.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:55.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This machine uses 4,000-yen balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この台は１玉4000円
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,4,000!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:58.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,4000円？\N普通の1000倍だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:59.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's a thousand times more than normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:03.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限りなくゼロに近い確率だが\N今 万が一当たれば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:05.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's almost impossible, but if he wins he'll have six or seven hundred million.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:05.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６億から７億
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:07.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… ７億？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Seven hundred million!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:10.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\Nマジかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:14.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ それ\N７億
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,700 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:17.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いたことねえぞ そんなパチンコ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:17.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of pachinko with those stakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:20.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,700 million what? 700 million perica?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:20.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,７億って７億ペリカか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ野郎　円に決まってるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:23.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way! It's gotta be yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:25.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,解放\Nああ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:30.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah! If Kaiji hits the jackpot, we're all free!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:29.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出れば間違いなく\N俺たち全員 解放だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:31.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん\Nカイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:34.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん\Nカイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:38.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If each ball is 4,000 yen, and Kaiji left with 800,000....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:36.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１玉4000円ってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:40.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんは80万持ってるから\N何発だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How many shots is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:45.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ　80万などという はした金\Nあの台じゃ２分で溶けるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:46.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can easily lose 800,000 on that machine in two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:48.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\Nそれじゃあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:48.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:53.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It looks like he came with 50 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:52.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴は元手として5000万という\N金を用意してきたそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,5000万？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,50 million!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:56.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやって そんな大金を？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How did he get that much money!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:14:01.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 高利の借金だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:59.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He borrowed it from a loan shark, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん… あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:11.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,At that moment, Kaiji's second Paqy card ran out—he's shot 20 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:08.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この時 カイジ　２枚目のパッキー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:13.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すなわち2000万を打ち尽くす
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お…\N追加だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Gimme another.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:19.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ\N迷わず３枚目のパッキーを購入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:19.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Unhesitatingly, Kaiji buys his third Paqy card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれでパッキーは３枚目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:24.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's his third Paqy card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:27.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's reaching the midpoint of his attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:27.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負は もう中盤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ焦りが出てくる頃だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Soon, he'll get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:31.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:33.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,焦り？\N当然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:36.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course. If he doesn't win he gets sent back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:36.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このまま当たりが来ずに終われば\Nここに逆戻り
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:45.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If that happens, it will take him more than a century to repay the money he's borrowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:40.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなった場合 上乗せになった\N借金から換算して
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:45.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴の終了年数は軽く100年を超える
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:47.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\N100？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:47.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A hundred...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A hundred years!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100年？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:53.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll be trapped here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:54.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり ここの住人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:58.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,For his whole life. Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:58.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生涯　お前たちもな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:07.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生涯 住人\Nそれはある意味 死より恐ろしい刑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:03.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The rest of one's life in the abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:06.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A fate more fearsome than death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:11.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最悪の宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The ultimate punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:13.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　頑張れ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:13.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:16.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ カイジさん\Nカイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:19.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張れ カイジさん\N頑張れ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Keep trying, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:18.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:26.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:26.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張れ\Nカイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:31.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝て　勝って抜けよう\Nこの地獄を一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:31.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Win... Win, and let's escape this hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:35.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:35.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　いけ　いけ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:37.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:38.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:43.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ カイジさん\Nいけ カイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:44.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:46.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エヘヘ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:55.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,See how pitiful those worms are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:54.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,醜く わめいておるのう\N地下の虫どもが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:57.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,のう？\Nはい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:59.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can hardly bear to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:16:01.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見苦しい 見苦しい\Nまったく なんてぶざまな姿だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:01.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:06.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アハハハ　分かるか お前たち\Nは？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:11.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You understand why I'm allowing them a television now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:12.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ わしがあの地下のクズどもに\Nテレビを見せることを許したか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:14.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？い… いや
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:19.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… それはその\Nいや その何というか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:19.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's, uh, how shall I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:23.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,す… すいません\Nアハハハ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無力\Nは？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:25.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Powerlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:30.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To show you how powerless they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:30.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無力であることを\N知ってもらうためじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:33.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,祈り 応援 そんなものの無力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:33.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Their prayers, their cheers, these do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:38.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I want you to know just how weak they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:39.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いかに効力がないかを\Nお前らに知ってもらいたいのじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:44.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're nothing but the superstitions of scum like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:44.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんなものはクズどもの気休め\N浅はかな迷信よ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:46.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に言うなら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:51.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you ever reach the point where you need to pray, you're already a failure of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:51.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,祈るようになったら\N人間も終わりという話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:57.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ　出んじゃろう\Nあの沼は出ん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It won't pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:57.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Bog won't pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:17:00.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれはクズどものヒーローに\N出せる台ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:17:03.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It won't pay to their hero. They're wasting their time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:03.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,所詮 無理な話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:08.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That machine pays only to men who are already made!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:08.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは功成り名を遂げた者だけが\N出せる名機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:12.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not just to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:12.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰でもというわけにはいかぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:16.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ　コケか真か
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Truth or lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:21.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その人間の持つ運 才能 性質 器量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:24.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A man's luck, his talent, his nature, his talent... All these make him a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:24.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すなわち人間の器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:30.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And the Bog judges them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:30.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさにその器を測る台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:38.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sadly for Kaiji, it will find him lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:34.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残念じゃが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:38.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,力不足じゃろう カイジ君では
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:40.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:41.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん\N頑張れ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:41.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:46.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Their path is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:47.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 こいつらの道 未来も\N閉ざされる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人頼み 神頼みで声援を送れば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:56.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These pitiful fools have no future if they cast their lot in with other men, or with God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:57.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,祈りが通じると思っている\N哀れなクズどもの未来がな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:06.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Worms like these don't even have the right to dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:02.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも地下に落ちた虫けらに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:06.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,未来を夢見る資格などない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:09.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ない　ない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:09.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:13.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　カイジさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:13.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:16.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４５組の熱狂とは対照的に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:21.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In contrast to the 45s' burning passion, a chill envelops the spectators at the casino!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:21.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼を囲む見物人たちの間には\N次第に しらけた空気
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:25.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,空しさ 虚脱感が漂い始める
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:25.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They begin to give up, become despondent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:36.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pointless acts! Fruitless effort! Foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:37.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意味のない行為 実らぬ努力\Nまさに愚行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:41.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They see Kaiji's determination as nothing but foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:41.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らにはカイジの執着が\Nまさに愚行にしか見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:44.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あーあ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:47.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The audience begins to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:48.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに その場を\N離れ始めるギャラリー
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:52.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:53.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人　２人　３人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:56.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつけばカイジの周りには
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:19:00.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When Kaiji looks up, he sees only Endoh, Sakazaki, and an audience of three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:19:00.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坂崎 遠藤らの他には\Nわずか３人のギャラリー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:04.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The only others left are the casino staff and Ichijou!
