Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:28.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だがしかし つぎ込む\Nひたすら つぎ込み続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:31.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But! But! He keeps shooting! Keeps shooting the 4,000-yen balls!
