Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:43.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It does not open! It will not open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:44.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開かない　開かない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:48.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開かない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It will not open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:56.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All he can do is pound on the unyielding door!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:51.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,微動だにしない その扉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:54.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに打つ　打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:56.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打ち続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:05.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Can this wasteful act bring him victory!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:03.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この一見 不毛な行為に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:06.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝算はあるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:10.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジに残された\Nシャバでの猶予は あと４時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:10.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji has only four hours left outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:13.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,240分を切る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:13.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The 240 minute mark passes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:17.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 間に合うのか　カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:16.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Will Kaiji make it in time!?
